    <section class="story-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="story-grid">
                <div class="story-content">
                    <span class="section-tag">Our Story</span>
                    <h2>Rooted in Faith, <br>Reaching Ethiopia and the World</h2>
                    <p>Faith Bible International Church was founded in Gerji, Addis Ababa, with a simple vision: to create a community where people could encounter God through His Word and experience authentic relationships.</p>
                    <p>Today, we continue to hold fast to our core values: the authority of Scripture, the power of prayer, the importance of community, and the urgency of the Great Commission.</p>
                </div>
